  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective, multicenter, observational study will evaluate the use of concomitant
      glucocorticoid therapy in adults with rheumatoid arthritis (RA) being treated with
      tocilizumab in daily clinical practice. Participants will be observed for up to 52 weeks
      after starting treatment with tocilizumab. All visits and assessments will be performed as
      per routine clinical practice, with no study-specific visits or interventions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
